description:
Focused on pencil art

using the regular prompts sometimes results in unexpected outcomes… i’ve tried running it with common prompts, such as manga, comic or vector, anime, etc.

modelVersions.name: v3 Safetenser
modelVersions.description:
Revamped from the ground up with the same training images however, the base model is now using openjourneyv4.

Train this model using the Same trigger word as before, but being that it's more mid journey themed... It's a little bit more diverse as far as environment creation and character design as it now leans more towards the realistic side.

You can counter actors of course with using negative prompts
